        <abstract> 
<p>Has received letter from Appleton’s that they agree to reprint from the latest edition of the <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> [5th English] and will add corrections sent by CD.</p>  
<p>They wish also to receive early sheets of new book [<hi rend="italic">Descent</hi>] on which they will pay £10.</p>  
<p>Will send cheque for sales of <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi>, based on older agreement between Appleton’s and Asa Gray to pay CD 5%.</p> 
        </abstract>
